- You sure had us worried. - I was just takin' five.
害我们都担心死了 嗯，闹着玩嘛

1074
01:12:44,986 --> 01:12:47,362
You know, playin' it cool.
就像是耍酷啊

1075
01:12:48,114 --> 01:12:51,408
- But he was too easy. - Good old Papa Bear.
逗着你们玩的 我亲爱的熊爸爸

1076
01:12:52,452 --> 01:12:55,162
It's going to be a bit dull without the Little Bloke, isn't it?
那小家伙要走了 我会想他的，你呢？

1077
01:12:55,663 --> 01:12:57,956
Yeah. So what we gonna do?
会啊，现在做什么啊？

1078
01:12:58,416 --> 01:13:01,543
I don't know... Now, don't start that again!
我不知道……嗯 你不要又来了，好不好啊？

1079
01:13:02,920 --> 01:13:06,131
Hey, Baggy. Too bad you missed the action.
嘿，巴希拉 你错过一场好戏了

1080
